WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.279
Excuse me.

00:00:02.377 --> 00:00:05.163
Could you tell me how to?

00:00:05.380 --> 00:00:08.914
How to get onto the platform?
Not to worry, dear.

00:00:09.133 --> 00:00:11.588
It's Ron's first time
to Hogwarts as well.

00:00:11.802 --> 00:00:17.721
All you do is walk straight at the wall
between platforms 9 and 10.

00:00:17.932 --> 00:00:21.384
- Best to run if you're nervous.
- Good luck.

